quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,26,"Munibuke ubwo mwari bake b’abanyantege nke mu gihugu (cya Maka), mutinya ko abantu (b’abahakanyi) babashimuta, maze (Allah) akabaha ubuhungiro (i Madina), akabashyigikiza inkunga ye ndetse akanabaha amafunguro meza kugira ngo mubashe gushimira"
  8,27,"Yemwe abemeye! Ntimugahemukire Allah n’Intumwa (Muhamadi), ndetse ntimukanahemuke mucunga nabi ibyo mwaragijwe kandi mubizi (ko ari icyaha)"
  8,28,"Munamenye ko imitungo yanyu n’urubyaro rwanyu ari ibigeragezo, kandi ko mu by’ukuri kwa Allah hari ibihembo bihambaye"
  8,29,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimutinya Allah, azabashoboza gutandukanya ikibi n’icyiza, abahanagureho ibyaha byanyu ndetse anabababarire. Kandi Allah ni Nyiringabire zihambaye"
  8,30,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo abahakanye bagucuriraga imigambi yo kugira ngo bakugire imbohe, cyangwa ngo bakwice, cyangwa ngo bakumeneshe. Bacuraga imigambi Allah agacura indi (myiza yo kuburizamo iya bo); kandi Allah ni we Uhebuje mu kuburizamo imigambi mibisha"
  8,31,N’iyo basomewe amagambo yacu (Qur’an) baravuga bati “Erega twarayumvise”; n’iyo dushaka twari kuvuga ameze nka yo. Ibi nta cyo biri cyo usibye kuba ari inkuru z’abo hambere.”
  8,32,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo bavugaga bati “Mana Nyagasani! Niba koko iyi (Qur’an) ari ukuri kuguturutseho, ngaho tugusheho imvura y’amabuye iturutse mu kirere, cyangwa utuzanire ibihano bibabaza"
  8,33,"Kandi Allah ntiyari kubahana mu gihe (wowe Muhamadi) ukibarimo, ndetse nta n’ubwo Allah yari kubahana mu gihe basaba imbabazi"